## Pipeline Summary

| Phase | What happens | Agent calls |
|-------|-------------|-------------|
| 1. Detect Mode | Classify query into 1 of 4 modes | 0 |
| 2. Multi-Angle Research | 3 parallel searches (official, practitioner, contrarian) | 3 |
| 3. Consolidate | Merge into mode-specific artifact with confidence tags | 1 |
| 4. Source Quality Filter | Audit sources, apply recency gates, adjust confidence | 1 |
| 5. Three-Reviewer Eval | Fresh verification (with veto) + completeness + actionability | 3 |
| 6. Merge + Gate | Hierarchical merge (A→B→C), tie-breaker if needed | 1-2 |
| 7. Deliver | Final artifact with all tags and annotations | 0 |
| **Total** | | **~9-10 calls** |

Estimated time: 2-4 minutes in claude.ai | ~1 minute in Claude Code (parallel execution). Add ~30 seconds if tie-breaker protocol activates.
